                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold color-copy">Price</h3>
                            <p class="color-copy font-['Hanken_Grotesk',sans-serif]">
                                Typical acquisitions range from $250k to $5 million+.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Item -->
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-8">
                        <div class="bg-[#E3BA63] rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                            <svg width="20" height="16" role="presentation" viewBox="0 0 20 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M17.9852 14.2207H19.7614V15.998H0.222656V14.2207H1.99891V0.890624C1.99891 0.641796 2.08476 0.431478 2.25646 0.259667C2.42817 0.0878572 2.63836 0.00195217 2.88703 0.00195217H11.7683C12.017 0.00195217 12.2271 0.0878572 12.3988 0.259667C12.5706 0.431478 12.6564 0.641796 12.6564 0.890624V14.2207H16.2089V7.11133H14.4327V5.33398H17.097C17.3457 5.33398 17.5559 5.41989 17.7276 5.5917C17.8993 5.76351 17.9852 5.97383 17.9852 6.22266V14.2207ZM3.77516 1.7793V14.2207H10.8802V1.7793H3.77516ZM5.55141 7.11133H9.10391V8.88867H5.55141V7.11133ZM5.55141 3.55664H9.10391V5.33398H5.55141V3.55664Z" fill="white"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold color-copy">Type</h3>
                            <p class="color-copy font-['Hanken_Grotesk',sans-serif]">
                                Hospitality, Real Estate, Insurance, Technology and Retail.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Item -->
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="bg-[#E3BA63] rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                            <svg width="16" height="20" role="presentation" viewBox="0 0 16 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M7.99215 17.1448L12.3795 12.737C13.1847 11.9431 13.7294 11.0071 14.0136 9.92881C14.286 8.87425 14.286 7.81969 14.0136 6.76514C13.7294 5.68688 13.1877 4.74785 12.3884 3.94805C11.5891 3.14824 10.6506 2.60615 9.57301 2.32178C8.5191 2.04925 7.46519 2.04925 6.41129 2.32178C5.33369 2.60615 4.39524 3.14824 3.59593 3.94805C2.79662 4.74785 2.25486 5.68688 1.97066 6.76514C1.6983 7.81969 1.6983 8.87425 1.97066 9.92881C2.25486 11.0071 2.79958 11.9431 3.60481 12.737L7.99215 17.1448ZM7.99215 19.6509L2.34367 13.9989C1.31345 12.9799 0.620711 11.7713 0.265461 10.3731C-0.0897891 9.02236 -0.0897891 7.67158 0.265461 6.3208C0.620711 4.92262 1.31049 3.71107 2.33479 2.68613C3.3591 1.6612 4.56991 0.965071 5.96722 0.597754C7.31717 0.254133 8.66712 0.254133 10.0171 0.597754C11.4144 0.965071 12.6252 1.6612 13.6495 2.68613C14.6738 3.71107 15.3636 4.92262 15.7188 6.3208C16.0741 7.67158 16.0741 9.02236 15.7188 10.3731C15.3636 11.7713 14.6708 12.9799 13.6406 13.9989L7.99215 19.6509ZM7.99215 10.1243C8.31187 10.1243 8.60792 10.0443 8.88027 9.88437C9.15263 9.72441 9.36874 9.50817 9.52861 9.23564C9.68847 8.96312 9.7684 8.66689 9.7684 8.34697C9.7684 8.02705 9.68847 7.73083 9.52861 7.4583C9.36874 7.18577 9.15263 6.96953 8.88027 6.80957C8.60792 6.64961 8.31187 6.56963 7.99215 6.56963C7.67242 6.56963 7.37638 6.64961 7.10402 6.80957C6.83167 6.96953 6.61555 7.18577 6.45569 7.4583C6.29583 7.73083 6.2159 8.02705 6.2159 8.34697C6.2159 8.66689 6.29583 8.96312 6.45569 9.23564C6.61555 9.50817 6.83167 9.72441 7.10402 9.88437C7.37638 10.0443 7.67242 10.1243 7.99215 10.1243ZM7.99215 11.9017C7.3527 11.9017 6.76062 11.7417 6.2159 11.4218C5.67118 11.1019 5.23896 10.6694 4.91924 10.1243C4.59951 9.57926 4.43965 8.98385 4.43965 8.33809C4.43965 7.69232 4.59951 7.09987 4.91924 6.56074C5.23896 6.02161 5.67118 5.59209 6.2159 5.27217C6.76062 4.95225 7.3527 4.79228 7.99215 4.79