                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold color-copy">Location</h3>
                            <p class="color-copy font-['Hanken_Grotesk',sans-serif]">
                                Westchester, New York City and Fairfield County, Connecticut with an emphasis on desirable neighborhoods.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Two-Tone Section Separator -->
        <div class="w-full overflow-hidden">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 1512 153"><path fill="#fff" d="M0 8h1512v145H0z"/><path fill="#CD962B" d="M800.5 46 1512 6v139L800.5 46Z"/><path fill="#F4F3F3" d="M0 11.917V0h1512v11.917L327 72 0 11.917Z"/></svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Investment & Acquisition Partners -->
		<section class="px-4 py-16 bg-white color-copy font-['Hanken_Grotesk',sans-serif]">
			<div class=" max-width mx-auto text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-4">
				Investment &amp; Acquisition Partners
				</h2>
				<div class="w-20 h-1 mx-auto bg-[#E3BA63] mb-6"></div>
				<p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
				We've built strong relationships with industry leaders across multiple sectors to provide comprehensive support for our portfolio companies.
				</p>

				<div class="mt-12 flex flex-row flex-wrap sm:flex-nowrap space-x-4 justify-center">
					<div class="flex h-22 xs:basis-1/3 w-100 md:basis-1/5 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-orange-50 mb-4">
						<img src="thetacoproject-logo.webp" alt="The Taco Project" class="object-contain" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="72" height="70" />
					</div>
					<div class="flex h-22 xs:basis-1/3 px-4 w-100 md:basis-1/5 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-orange-50 mb-4">
						<img src="april-marin-logo.webp" alt="April Marin" class="object-contain" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="146" height="51" />
					</div>
					<div class="flex h-22 xs:basis-1/3 px-4 w-100 md:basis-1/5 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-orange-50 mb-4">
						<img src="airbnb-logo.webp" alt="Airbnb" class="object-contain" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="162" height="108" />
					</div>
					<div class="flex h-22 xs:basis-1/3 px-4 w-100 md:basis-1/5 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-orange-50 mb-4">
						<img src="gipper-logo.webp" alt="Gipper" class="object-contain" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="149" height="40" />
					</div>
					<div class="flex h-22 xs:basis-1/3 px-4 w-100 md:basis-1/5 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-orange-50 mb-4">
						<img src="credready-logo.webp" alt="CredReady" class="object-contain" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="146" height="45" />
					</div>
				</div>
            </div>
		</section>




    
        <!-- Section Separator -->
		<div class="w-full overflow-hidden -mb-[2px] z-1" style="z-index: 10;">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  role="presentation" fill="none" preserveAspectRatio="none" viewBox="0 0 682 50" class="w-full aspect-[682/50]"><path fill="#1A1919" d="M0 44.796h224.176L682 0v50H0v-5.204Z"/></svg>
        </div>


        <!-- family-owned section -->
		<section class="bg-[#1A1919] text-white px-4 py-20 z-2" style="z-index: 20;">
            <div class=" max-width mx-auto">
                <!-- Heading -->
                <div class="text-center mb-12">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl">
                        Family Owned &amp; Operated Since 1977
                    </h2>
                    <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-[#E3BA63] mt-4 mx-auto"></div>
                </div>
                <!-- Content grid -->
                 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start">
                    <!-- Image -->
                     <div>
                        <img src="trion-holdings-family-owned.webp" alt="Family Photo" class="w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="840" height="556" />
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Text Content -->
                    <div class="space-y-6  text-white text-base leading-relaxed">
                        <p>
                            Throughout our 40 year history, Trion has developed a full service investment firm which benefits from in-house underwriting, property management, and asset management. Trion’s success has been driven by implementing conservative underwriting policies along with a hands on asset management approach.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Upon acquisition we will work with the leadership team to analyze the current operational policies and procedures and offer cost saving and time management strategies that can increase the scalability and efficiency of the business.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Trion Holding's past purchases have benefited from a range of post-acquisition enhancements including but not limited to light cosmetic upgrades, management improvements, larger projects with extensive gut renovations, complete management and rent roll overhauls, as well as property rebranding.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Section Separator -->
        <div class="w-full overflow-hidden -mt-[2px]">
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation" class="w-full aspect-[1512/290]" preserveAspectRatio="none" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 1512 290"><path fill="#fff" d="M0 5h1512v285H0z"/><path fill="#E3BA63" d="m0 78 1036.5 48.5-7.5 51L0 287V78Z"/><path fill="#1A1919" d="M0 58V.5h1512v10L1280 203 0 81V58Z"/></svg>
		</div>


        
		
        
        



    <script>
      // small script to set footer year and manage splash screen similar to original
      document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
        const splashScreen = document.getElementById('splash-screen');
        const yearEl = document.getElementById('year');
    if (yearEl) yearEl.textContent = String(new Date().getFullYear());
        if (splashScreen) {
          setTimeout(() => { splashScreen.classList.add('hidden'); }, 2600);
        }
      });
    </script>
  </main>
</Base>
